title: THE MANDALORIAN Season 2 Episode 2 Breakdown, Ending Explained, and Theories!
author: Think Story
comment:
😋 Damn, Baby Yoda straight up munchin' on those eggs... hope Frog Lady doesn't find out.🥚🥚
For more Mandalorian videos click here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7iB3-JitOOncA-oLH2AD-Tq

The story of:
-1 good dad
-1 good mom
-1 bad 50-year-old
As a person with a fear of frogs and spiders I was appropriately horrified. 😂
This episode has me convinced Baby Yoda is on the dark side. He was gleefully indulging in trying to end the frog lady's bloodline.

Did anyone notice, the Giant parent spider seemed to break two of the Lazer Crest's cockpit window panes? 
You hear the glass break and see the shards fly as the spider punches through. 
Then when you see the wide shot of Din Jarin beginning repairs, there seems to be no broken glass panes around the cockpit.
